{"id":1287,"date":"2024-08-04T18:40:10","date_gmt":"2024-08-04T18:40:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1287"},"modified":"2024-08-04T18:40:10","modified_gmt":"2024-08-04T18:40:10","slug":"mission-082","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-082\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #082: Weed Whacker"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Mission #082: Weed Whacker<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Grim Woods &#8211; man west of east entrance<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Defeat the Dehara City Gym<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Cut down all the grass in Grim Woods<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>Beedrillite<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>There\u2019s a rich man in Grim Woods who wants all the grass cut down so he can build something. If you assist, he\u2019ll give you a Beedrillite mega stone.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/082\/01-pokemon-unbound-grim-woods-entrance-from-the-dresco-town-side.jpg\" alt=\"Grim Woods entrance from the Dresco Town side \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Grim Woods entrance from the Dresco Town side<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Grim Woods can be accessed from Dresco Town by heading across the southwest bridge.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/082\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-man-only-appears-after-the-dehara-gym.jpg\" alt=\"The man only appears after the Dehara Gym \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The man only appears after the Dehara Gym<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After acquiring Surf and defeating the Dehara City Gym, a rich man will appear in the middle of Grim Woods with a mission for you.<\/p>\n<p>He wants you to Cut down all the long grass in Grim Woods.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/082\/03-pokemon-unbound-cutting-down-long-grass.jpg\" alt=\"Cutting down long grass \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Cutting down long grass<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>A Pok\u00e9mon who can use <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm01-cut\/\">Cut<\/a> just needs to be in your party for you to be able to use it, if you\u2019ve got the HM. You just need to activate it from the Pok\u00e9mon team menu.<\/p>\n<p>There is a lot of long grass in Grim Woods, and it will take some considerable time to cut it all down, considering you can only do it in a 3&#215;3 grid at one time.<\/p>\n<p>If you manage to do it though, the rich man will give you the Beedrillite.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/082\/04-pokemon-unbound-the-reward-for-cutting-all-that-grass.jpg\" alt=\"The reward for cutting all that grass \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The reward for cutting all that grass<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1288,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1287","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1287","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1288"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1287"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1287"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}